  path_stag INT64,

CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.idc_v14.quantitative_measurements`
(
  PatientID STRING,
  SOPInstanceUID STRING,
  SeriesDescription STRING,
  measurementGroup_number INT64 OPTIONS(description="Measurement group number corresponding to the measurement groups within the TID 1500 report, starting from 0."),
  segmentationInstanceUID STRING OPTIONS(description="SOPInstanceUID of the segmentation object defining the region of interest corresponding to the measurement."),
  segmentationSegmentNumber ARRAY<INT64> OPTIONS(description="SegmentNumber of the segment within the segmentation object referenced by segmentationInstanceUID defining the region of interest corresponding to the measurement."),
  sourceSegmentedSeriesUID STRING OPTIONS(description="SeriesInstanceUID corresponding to the image series over which the measurement was done."),
  trackingIdentifier STRING OPTIONS(description="Value of the TID 1500 Measurement group row corresponding to the concept \"Tracking Identifier\" (e.g., row 2 in TID 1411)"),
  trackingUniqueIdentifier STRING OPTIONS(description="Value of the TID 1500 Measurement group row corresponding to the concept \"Tracking Unique Identifier\" (e.g., row 3 in TID 1411)"),
  Quantity STRUCT<CodeValue STRING, CodingSchemeDesignator STRING, CodeMeaning STRING> OPTIONS(description="Value of the concept code corresponding to TID 1500 Measurement group row where VT is NUM."),
  derivationModifier STRUCT<CodeValue STRING, CodingSchemeDesignator STRING, CodeMeaning STRING> OPTIONS(description="Value corresponding to the concept \"Derivation\" for the measurement within SR TID 1500 document (e.g., row 8 in TID 1419)"),
  Value NUMERIC OPTIONS(description="Value corresponding to the concept listed in the Quantity field."),
  Units STRUCT<CodeValue STRING, CodingSchemeDesignator STRING, CodingSchemeVersion STRING, CodeMeaning STRING> OPTIONS(description="Coded units for the value stored in the Value attribute."),
  finding STRUCT<CodeValue STRING, CodingSchemeDesignator STRING, CodingSchemeVersion STRING, CodeMeaning STRING> OPTIONS(description="Value of the TID 1500 Measurement group row corresponding to the concept \"Finding\" (e.g., row 3b in TID 1411)"),
  findingSite STRUCT<CodeValue STRING, CodingSchemeDesignator STRING, CodingSchemeVersion STRING, CodeMeaning STRING> OPTIONS(description="Value of the TID 1500 Measurement group row corresponding to the concept \"Finding Site\" (e.g., row 2 in TID 1419)")
)
OPTIONS(
  friendly_name="quantitative_measurements",
  description="A convenience view providing simplified access to the items within the DICOM SR TID 1500 documents that contain quantitative measurements. All attributes named following the CamelCase notation (except Quantity and Value) correspond to standard DICOM attributes and are documented in the DICOM standard; see source code for the underlying query at https://github.com/ImagingDataCommons/etl_flow/blob/master/bq/derived_table_creation/BQ_Table_Building/derived_data_views/sql/dicom_quantitative_measurements.sql",
  labels=[("tbd_key_1", "value_1"), ("tbd_key_2", "value_2")]
);
